name: Antonella Rose
introduction: Antonella Rose is best known for her unforgettable role on the last season of the AMC series, Fear the Walking Dead, playing Tracy Otto. She can also be seen in the Hulu series, Candy, opposite Jessica Biel and Melanie Lynskey. She recently acquired her first lead on the incredible up and coming independent feature film, A Sudden Case of Christmas, directed by Peter Chelsom, and opposite Danny DeVito and Wilmer Valderrama, coming this Christmas. Last but not least, she also wrapped on the most notorious horror movie of all time Terrifier 3 coming on theaters in October. Additional credits for Antonella include the Disney Channel series, Raven's Home.- IMDb Mini Biography By: PR agency
